{"tid":2307990,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"郭嘉銓：正調查巿民就媒體查冊報道其他報案","createTime":"2020-12-01T14:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T18:40:38.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ccaad45f27d22fa5b3c01495f4f00d60d93c99e3","tid":2307990,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T14:07:10.000Z","msg":"警察公共關係科總警司郭嘉銓今午（1日）出席一個網上研討會時表示，除香港電台《鏗鏘集》編導蔡玉玲因查冊被控外，警方還有收到個別人士就其他媒體使用查冊報道的報案，會視乎有否足夠證據作出檢控，警方目前正調查中。郭嘉銓又再度為修警例背書，強調警方沒有資格為傳媒工作者下定義，辯稱修改警例是為了監管警員。<br />\n<br />\n樹仁大學今午舉辦「新聞採訪的邊界？」網上研討會，郭嘉銓及記者協會主席楊健興均有參與，討論修改通例及查冊等議題。被問到香港電台《鏗鏘集》編導蔡玉玲因查冊被控一案，郭嘉銓透露有資料擁有人報案，經警方獲取證據，並徵詢律政司意見後，才作拘捕及檢控；郭又指有收到個別人士就個別媒體的查冊報道報案，強調須視乎有沒有足夠證據，警方目前正調查中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201201/Q3Y4V75PWVEUBKRUIJ7PKIUOY4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201201%2FQ3Y4V75PWVEUBKRUIJ7PKIUOY4%2F&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0tMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=04963f65\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201201%2FQ3Y4V75PWVEUBKRUIJ7PKIUOY4%2F&h=ee804209\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201201/Q3Y4V75PWVEUBKRUIJ7PKIUOY4/</a>"},{"pid":"fd84333f0b7ffa1ca949b901b2f41b2139288db8","tid":2307990,"uid":82938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T14:07:50.000Z","msg":"全部唔比查"},{"pid":"ff0124f317d8d0e2fba1c516057f1da0faf28864","tid":2307990,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T14:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50370db16312ba645e5c3b12f3e6d7e509443fc6","tid":2307990,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T14:14:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass